text.section:
A county seasonal farmer's market producer sampling license established under this section shall:
Be valid at all farmer's markets in the county;
Be valid at any public festival or event in the county;
Be valid for the entire season for which it is issued; and
Have a single fee as set by the county.

The Department shall adopt regulations that:
Establish eligibility for the license;
Provide for the authorized uses of the license;
Establish standards and approved methods under which sampling shall be conducted;
Specify the duration of the season during which the license is valid; and
Include other provisions that are necessary to protect public health and control foodborne illnesses.
